
 according to paper "The Bounded Retransmition Protocol must be on time!"
 basic structure:
 
	Producer				Consumer
	 |   ^					   ^
     Sin |   | Sout				   | Rout
	 v   |			     		   |
	Sender -----toK--------> K ---fromK----> Receiver
		<---timeout-----
		<-----fromL-------L <-----toL----


see. brp1.jpg, brp2.jpg


parameters:
REPEAT = maximal number of retransmitions
MAX_FRAMES = maximal number of frames
ERROR (0/1) = for 1 there with error (which I have done in modelling)

properties:
reachability of Consumer.st_error (unreachable should be, reachable with error)